Discord is a chat chat room designed for gamers. It's mainly used for like skype except it is easier to use and there is no viedo calling only voice channels. previously skype was the go to for gamers since skype also offered voice calling but skype is a bit complicated and not very gamer friendl as inviting people to a chat requires you to create a new chat. in discord everything is easier and more efficient and it doesnt take up as much ram on your computer.
